# 3f716575b4d84b90a2df186351b06b82
msgid "``permission`` is used to specify which rights will be granted to the ``principal``. The possible values are: ``:read``, ``:write``, ``read_execute``, ``:modify``, ``:full_control``,  and ``:deny``."
